{% extends 'templates/base.php' %}

{% block title %}{{ title }}{% endblock %}

{% block main %}
  <h1 class="section-title">{{ title }}</h1>
  <blockquote>
    <p>“The sole focus of Eastlake Elite Football is to develop the next generation athlete. The mission, to have an impact on the next generation, on and off the field, is what fuels our fire and gives us a sense of direction. Each athlete should want to take their abilities to the next level through dedication and hard work. This program will encourage hard work, teach fundamentals, and inspire the next generation of athletes to be great athletes and wonderful people”</p>
  </blockquote>
  <h3 class="section-sub-title">Youth Camps</h3>
  <p>We are happy to offer a youth football camp for 1st-4th grade athletes! This camp will teach your youngster the basics of the game, focus on hand eye coordination, and have fun. These camps are seasonal, please call the club!</p>
  <h3 class="section-sub-title">Middle School Quarterback &amp; Receiver Camps</h3>
  <p>Much like our youth football camp, the middle school quarterback and receiver camp will focus on many of the basic techniques for throwing and pass catching. The camp will build off those concepts and begin to delve into upper level skills and football IQ. It is also our vision to develop high character in each one of the athletes and instill in them a desire for hard work. Please call the club for more information.</p>
  <h3 class="section-sub-title">Elite High School Quarterback Camps</h3>
  <p>Our High School Quarterback Camps are the cream of the crop for quarterback training in the great Michiana area. The camps are designed to test high school quarterbacks mentally and physically. Each session is in the mold of a college practice full of drills aimed to increase arm strength, increase foot quickness, add balance, develop a sense of urgency, and create a sense of ownership. Please call the club for more info!</p>
{% endblock %}